<!--
    Samsung Galaxy A90 5G (r3q) integer/array overrides

    AUTO-BRIGHTNESS MAPPING:
    These arrays map ambient light sensor lux values to display
    brightness levels (0-255). Extracted from stock One UI 4.1
    vendor RRO (framework-res__auto_generated_rro_vendor.apk)
    on SM-A908NKSU5EXE1 (Android 12, S6E3FC2 AMOLED panel).

    Stock source: 28 lux thresholds + 28 backlight values.
    These are the exact values Samsung calibrates for this panel.
-->
